# Tuples

```scala
val t2 = (1, "hello")
println(t2._1)
println(t2._2)

val t3 = (3.14, true, "world")
println(t3._1)
println(t3._2)
println(t3._3)

val pairs = List((1, "one"), (2, "two"), (3, "three"))
pairs.foreach { case (n, s) => println(s"$n=$s") }

val swapped = pairs.map { case (n, s) => (s, n) }
swapped.foreach { case (s, n) => println(s"$s:$n") }
```
